IntroText: What do you want? (She stares at you.)
Amazing!  I've wanted to tie her for weeks.|Now what do you want? (She stares at you.)
(She stares at the girl with the brown hair.)
(She crosses her arms and looks at you in the eyes.)
(She stares again at the girl with the brown hair.)
(She turns her head and ignores you.)
Class will begin soon but let's talk later.
Don't talk to me bitch!|(She turns her head and ignores you.)
Congrats on humiliating her.  Let's talk after class.|(She looks at Amanda and gives a thumbs up.)
Fuck!  You were looking in my bag?|(She seems nervous that you found the ropes.)
(She makes a curious face at you.)
Did you steal these ropes from my bag?|(She looks furious.)
Wait until I get out!|(She struggles in vain to get free.)
At least she looks more humiliated than me.|(She looks at Amanda and grins.)
You thief!  We have nothing to talk about.
I can't believe you tied me up in here.|We'll talk about it later.
I can't believe you tied me up in here.|On the bright side, she's still in trouble.
